{"title":"Remco’s Golden Steed: Limited Edition ‘Golden Season’ S-Works Tarmac SL8","link":"https://bikerumor.com/golden-season-s-works-tarmac-sl8/","date":1747085820000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-snow--1536x1025.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1025\" alt=\"Remco Golden Tarmac SL8 Road snow\" /></p>\n<p>Remco Evenepoel doesn’t just race in gold — now he <em>rides</em> it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Specialized just released a shimmering tribute to one of the peloton’s brightest stars with the S-Works Tarmac SL8 ‘Golden Season’ LTD, a limited-run race machine celebrating Remco’s palmarès and Specialized’s Golden Anniversary. Only 272 lucky riders worldwide will get the chance to swing a leg over this stunner — the same rig that Remco will be racing in 2025, dripping in carbon and gold. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>S-Works Tarmac SL8 Golden Season LTD road bike</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1708\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Remco Golden Tarmac SL8 Road\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-1536x1025.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(All photos/Specialized)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>So get your Austin Powers Goldmember impressions ready; there is a lot of gooooold coming.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>‘Make the Break’… But Make It Gold</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-top-scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-top-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Remco Golden Tarmac SL8 Road full top\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-top-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-top-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-top-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-top-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-top-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-top-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-top-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-top-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’ve been watching the Soudal Quick-Step squad this season, you’ve seen their <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@soudalquickstepteam\" target=\"_blank\">‘Make the Break’</a> motif streak across Europe in red and white. The ‘Golden Season’ LTD version? It flips that script. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The same wave graphic morphs into a liquid gold flow, wrapping the <strong><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/speed-sniffer-specialized-tarmac-sl8-aero-road-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">Tarmac SL8</a></strong>’s carbon core with a two-tone metallic fade that’s all flash with just the right amount of stealth tucked underneath.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Subtle nods to Remco’s career decorate the top tube — his name, the unmistakable Wolfpack logo, and a few cues to his growing list of accolades. The whole aesthetic reads fast, standing still. This thing’s a museum piece you’ll want to race.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Gold-Plated Performance</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-jpg-scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1708\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-jpg-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Remco Golden Tarmac SL8 Road jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-jpg-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-jpg-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-jpg-1536x1025.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-jpg-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-jpg-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-jpg-2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-jpg-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-jpg-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/specialized-s-works-ares-2-road-cycling-race-shoe/\" target=\"_blank\">Gold-soled Specialized Ares 2 shoes</a>,<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/specialized-s-works-ares-2-road-cycling-race-shoe/\" target=\"_blank\"> sold separately. </a></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Under all that gold leaf is a bona fide WorldTour weapon:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Frame:</strong> Specialzed S-Works Tarmac SL8</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheels:</strong> Roval Rapide CLX II with oversized Team-only graphics</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Cockpit:</strong> Roval Rapide bars/stem, again with matching Team graphics</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Saddle:</strong> S-Works Power with Mirror 3D-printed tech</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Drivetrain:</strong> Shimano Dura-Ace Di2, because of course it is!</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Price: $15,000</strong>… what a bargain.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-sale--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-sale--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Remco Golden Tarmac SL8 Road sale\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-sale--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-sale--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-sale--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-sale--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-sale--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-sale--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-sale--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is the <strong><em>exact </em></strong>same setup Remco will pilot through the 2025 calendar, and Specialized isn’t cutting corners. If you’re wondering how limited this actually is — Specialized is keeping it to <strong>272 total builds</strong>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s <em>worldwide</em>. After that? Gone.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-back-side--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-back-side--1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Remco Golden Tarmac SL8 Road\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-back-side--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-back-side--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-back-side--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-back-side--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-back-side--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-back-side--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-top-drive--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-top-drive--1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Remco Golden Tarmac SL8 Road top drive\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-top-drive--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-top-drive--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-top-drive--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-top-drive--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-top-drive--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-top-drive--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Only One Way In</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You won’t find the ‘Golden Season’ LTD on your local shop floor unless they’re part of Specialized’s premium global retailer network — and even then, the only way to buy is through Specialized.com. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you place the order, your gold SL8 will be hand-delivered through Specialized’s premium delivery service. Expect concierge-level treatment for a bike that rides like royalty.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-kit--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1708\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-kit--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Remco Golden Tarmac SL8 Road full kit\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-kit--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-kit--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-kit--1536x1025.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-kit--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-kit--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-kit--2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-kit--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Remco-Golden-Tarmac-SL8-Road-full-kit--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Remco might not have the rainbow stripes anymore in 2025, but he’s still riding high with a bike like this under him. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This Tarmac SL8 ‘Golden Season’ LTD isn’t just a bike — it’s a rolling tribute to one of the most explosive riders of this generation, and a fitting exclamation point on Specialized’s 50th year in the game.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.specialized.com/us/en/s-works-tarmac-sl8-ltd-remcos-golden-season/p/4293757?color=5467127-4293757\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Specialized.com </em></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/golden-season-s-works-tarmac-sl8/\">Remco’s Golden Steed: Limited Edition ‘Golden Season’ S-Works Tarmac SL8</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"d81035a747d4f2a0dfe0a093dd5eca7a77b82962fe7fbf65268941f0ab7ffdce","category":"Cycling"}